android:pivotY="50%"
android:startOffset="0"
android:toXScale="0.85"
android:toYScale="0.85" />
</set>
</code></pre> <p>I think the problem is that when you go from A to B, A goes to background and it is still alive, so when you come back from B to A, <code>overridePendingTransition</code> won't work for A. As <a href="http://developer.android.com/reference/android/app/Activity.html#overridePendingTransition%28int,%20int%29" rel="nofollow">documentation</a> says about <code>overridePendingTransition</code>:</p>
<blockquote>
