Maps v2 marker animation - fade in and out <p>How would one fade in and out a <a href="http://developer.android.com/reference/com/google/android/gms/maps/GoogleMap.html" rel="nofollow">GoogleMap</a> <a href="http://developer.android.com/reference/com/google/android/gms/maps/model/Marker.html" rel="nofollow">marker</a>?</p>
